data.description:
GREAT location in Surprise one street over from Marley Park!  This spacious home is a split floor plan, with large master on one side and 3 bedrooms on the other.  The spacious kitchen with granite counters & stylish backsplash, lots of storage, and a breakfast bar/island flows into the family room with an exit to the screened in patio for enjoying the cooler months to come.  The living/dining rooms offer plenty of space for a game room or formal living/dining.  The master bedroom and bath offer plenty of closet space, garden tub and separate shower.  
Front and backyards have easy to maintain landscaping and are ready for your personal touch. RV Gate.
Located in the heart of Surprise close to shopping, sport venues, and entertainment.
